<%= content_for :body_class, "bg-gray-800" %>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="container hero__content relative">
    <h1 class="hero__heading font-extrabold text-6xl text-gray-800 leading-none">
      Your personal newsletter
    </h1>
    <h2 class="hero__subheading text-gray-500">
      The web is open, via RSS you can follow a website, blog or profile on the internet and get a
      periodical update by email.
    </h2>

    <div class="home-chrome-wrapper md:absolute right-0 top-0 md:mt-40" style="right: 80px">
      <% unless Rails.env.test? %>
        <%= render "chrome" do %>
          <iframe src="/example-email?no_index=true" class="flex-grow w-full" data-controller="example"></iframe>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <%= link_to "Get started", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn--primary-outline mb-2" %>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<div class="bg-gray-200">
  <div class="container max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-wrap px-4">
    <div class="w-full sm:w-1/3 pr-8 py-16 sm:py-16">
      <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-white bg-blue-500 rounded-full">1</span>
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-semibold">Create an account</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">It's as simple as entering your email address and picking a password.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="w-full sm:w-1/3 pr-8 py-16 sm:py-16">
      <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-white bg-purple-500 rounded-full">2</span>
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-semibold">Add websites</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">Click the big button and start adding feeds to your account. Public instagram profiles are also supported.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="w-full sm:w-1/3 py-8 sm:py-16">
      <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-white bg-indigo-500 rounded-full">3</span>
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-semibold">Receive the email</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">From now on you will receive a daily email with the new content you subscribed to, from your account you can change the sites you follow at any time.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-white text-center pt-10 pb-5">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <%= render "shared/supported_platforms" %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-200">
  <div class="container max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 sm:py-16">
    <p class="mb-2 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-blue-500">
      <%= I18n.t("customer", count: User.count) %> (and counting) can't be wrong</p>
    <h3 class="text-4xl leading-tight font-medium">

      <div class="testimonials text-base">
        <div class="testimonial">
          <p class="testimonial__content">
            “RSSMailer is great. At first just gave it a try since DenseDiscovery linked to it, but I now love reading my RSS feeds (blogs, news sites, YouTube channels)
            in my email app every morning. ”
          </p>

          <div class="testimonial__author">
            <%= image_tag "nicolas-magand.jpg", class: "testimonial__author-avatar" %>
            <div class="ml-3">
              <p class="testimonial__author-name">Nicolas Magand</p>
              <%= link_to "@nicolasmagand", "https://twitter.com/nicolasmagand/status/1174059304732766214?s=20", class: "testimonial__author-link" %>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="testimonial">
          <p class="testimonial__content">
            “I find that I like rssmailer.app!”
          </p>

          <div class="testimonial__author">
            <%= image_tag "erik-de-bruijn.png", class: "testimonial__author-avatar" %>
            <div class="ml-3">
              <p class="testimonial__author-name">Erik de Bruijn</p>
              <%= link_to "@ErikDeBruijn", "https://twitter.com/ErikDeBruijn/status/1174386736039747592?s=20", class: "testimonial__author-link" %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial">
          <p class="testimonial__content">
            “I'm using rssmailer.app to get new blog posts in my inbox<br>
            What RSS blogs should I add?<br>
            I prefer blogs from makers or independent writers”<br>
          </p>

          <div class="testimonial__author">
            <%= image_tag "adriaan-van-rossum.jpg", class: "testimonial__author-avatar" %>
            <div class="ml-3">
              <p class="testimonial__author-name">Adriaan van Rossum</p>
              <%= link_to "@AdriaanvRossum", "https://twitter.com/AdriaanvRossum/status/1165913377996189696", class: "testimonial__author-link" %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
  </div>


  <div class="bg-blue-800" style="background: radial-gradient(1270.42px at 0% 0%, #14355F 0%, #2C5282 100%)">
    <div class="container max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 text-center py-8 sm:py-32">
      <h3 class="mb-2 text-4xl leading-tight font-medium text-blue-100">Ready for that extra daily email?</h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-blue-200">Create an account and add some websites.</p>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <%= link_to "Get started", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn--primary-outline mb-2" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
